  {
    "type": "EXPOSITORY (ENGLISH BIBLE)",
    "name": "Benson Commentary",
    "elements": [
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "bld",
        "text": "Psalm 109:21-22",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "verse-link",
            "text": "Psalm 109:21-22",
            "children": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ". ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "But do thou for me, O God — ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "Namely, what I desire, which he expresses in the next clause, saying, ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "Deliver thou me — ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "Or, he means, ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "Do thou act for me; ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "be not silent or still, but stir up thyself to work on my behalf; ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "for thy name’s sake — ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "For the glory of thy faithfulness, which is highly concerned in giving me the deliverance which thou hast promised me; ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "because thy mercy is good — ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "That is, gracious, and ready to do good to all, but especially to those that love and fear thee. ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "For I am poor and needy — ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "And therefore a very proper object for thy pity and help. ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "And my heart is wounded within me ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "— I am wounded not slightly, but even to the very heart, with soul-piercing sorrows.",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "p",
